data.description: Lovely 4 Bedroom, 3.5 Bath, 3-Car Garage Home Located on a Beautiful Street in the Sought-After Neighborhood of Auburn Lakes Zoned to Excellent Klein Schools. Very Popular Open Floor Plan Features Soaring Ceilings, Extensive Hardwood Floors, Plantation Shutters in Front Windows, Roof, High Efficiency A/C Systems & Water Heater Replaced in 2022, Microwave, Fences & Carpet July '23.  Spacious Island Kitchen w/2-Story Ceiling & Windows Open to Breakfast & Family Room w/Gas Log Fireplace and Stairway w/Wrought-Iron Balusters.  1st Floor Primary Bedroom & Bath w/Jetted Tub, Separate Shower, Double Sinks & Large Walk-in Closet.  3 Generous Sized Bedrooms, 2 Full-Baths, Huge Private Game Room Plus 2 Outstanding Walk-In Attics Upstairs.  Wonderful Storage & Closet Space Thru-Out the Home. Flagstone Patio in the Backyard and Extra Yard Space on Each Side of the Home.  Great Location and Community with Lots of Amenities and Easy Access to the Grand Parkway, Shopping, Schools & Restaurants.
